<div class="modal hide fade" id="delNewsModal">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <a class="close" data-dismiss="modal">×</a>
    <h3 id="wintitle">删除新闻</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <div class="alert alert-error">
	  <strong>警告！</strong> 确认删除新闻?
